item.title: You Won't Believe What Happens When You Try Making This World Record Paper Plane!
item.description: 4 Conclusion: What you learned, any tips for others Introduction: What is a Paper Plane and What is a World Record? A paper plane is a type of model aircraft, usually constructed from a single sheet of paper or cardboard, and capable of sustained flight It is the simplest form of an aircraft to build and fly A world record is an officially recognized best achievement in a certain activity or sport, usually determined by a specific set of criteria.
